================================================================================
  Toaster_Features — Dashboard tile & widget ideas
  Vanguard CRM Dashboard (OnlyOffice CRM backend)
================================================================================

Naming: "Toaster" = things that pop up or surface attention on the workspace,
like toast notifications — quick-glance widgets users add via "Add Tile".

This list is inspired by patterns in widely used CRMs:

  - Salesforce Sales Cloud (Home widgets, Kanban, Activity timeline)
  - HubSpot CRM (Today view, Tasks, Deals, Activity feed)
  - Pipedrive (Pipeline, Activities, Insights)
  - Zoho CRM (Home components, Blueprint stages, Analytics)
  - Microsoft Dynamics 365 / Monday Sales CRM (boards + widgets)

Already implemented in this app (do not re-list as new):

  - Opportunity group tiles (filtered pipeline cards)
  - Tasks tile (hourly refresh)
  - Notifications / relationship feed tile
  - Calendar tiles (ICS / Proton)
  - Notes tiles (markdown, server-side save)
  - New Opportunity button
  - Deal edit modal (stage, due, tags, text event note)
  - Per-user layout & profiles on server


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
TIER 1 — High value, fits current APIs (recommended next)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Opportunity preview toaster (FEAT-001 in FUTURE_FEATURES.md)
   - Click card → popup with fields + last 10 history events.
   - Salesforce: "Record preview"; HubSpot: side peek; Pipedrive: deal detail.

2. Stale deals tile ❌ (FEAT-023 — scrapped in v1.8.0)
   - Attempted activity-based (feed only 30 days) and due-date-based (expectedCloseDate not reliably past-due).
   - Both approaches failed to list deals. See ISSUE-004 in ISSUES.md.
   - May revisit if CRM API provides last-modified timestamp.
   - Pipedrive: "Stuck deals"; HubSpot: idle deals reports.

3. Closing this week / month tile
   - Filter by expected close date in range (already have due on cards).
   - Salesforce: "Closing this month" list view.

4. My open tasks by due date
   - Variant of Tasks tile sorted by due, overdue highlighted.
   - HubSpot: task queue; Zoho: task home component.

5. Activity timeline tile (single group or global)
   - Last 20 history events across my opportunities (reuse history/filter).
   - Dynamics: Activity feed; Salesforce: Chatter/activity.

6. Win / loss summary counter
   - Count by stage type or closed-won/lost if API exposes stage category.
   - HubSpot: deal forecast summary.


