   - Total pipeline value, count open deals, avg deal size.
   - Salesforce: dashboard components; Monday: formula columns as KPIs.

8. Leaderboard / team workload
   - Open deals by responsible user (portal users + opportunity filter).
   - Salesforce: "Team pipeline".

9. Recent wins tile
   - Last 5 moved to won stage (history or stage change events).

10. Contact quick-view tile
    - Pin one contact: phone, email, linked opportunities (CRM contact API).

11. Documents / files tile
    - Recent files linked to opportunities (Files API — research like FEAT-003).
    - **Editable OnlyOffice embed:** see **FEAT-022** in FUTURE_FEATURES.md (link-out → Docs API embed; Shared Spreadsheet field).

12. Email / correspondence strip
    - If CRM mail module exposed: last emails per user (app already has mail parsing hints in feed code).

13. Duplicate / data quality alerts
    - Opportunities missing contact, due date, or required user fields.

14. Stage funnel mini-chart
    - Bar or funnel: count per stage for a saved filter group.
    - Pipedrive: pipeline conversion; HubSpot: funnel report (simplified).


